    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the style of Chinese painting that flourished at the beginning of the 17th century. The style is characterized by typically detailed, complicated compositions, executed in fine lines and delicate colors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al estilo de la pintura china que prosperó al principio del siglo XVII. El estilo es caracterizado por las composiciones típicamente detalladas, complicadas, ejecutadas en líneas finas y colores delicados.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de stijl van Chinese schilderkunst die een bloeiperiode doormaakte aan het begin van de 17de eeuw. De stijl wordt gekenmerkt door gedetailleerde, complexe composities met fijne lijnen en zachte kleuren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>用指興盛於十七世紀初的中國繪畫風格，以細膩線條作畫，多無色彩。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
